Private Property and EDPF Property Academy are proud to announce an in-person masterclass which is designed to equip the South African consumer market on how to purchase their first property. This first in-person event of its kind in SA, is set to impart vital knowledge and tools into attendees for buying their first home. Being hosted on 25th June 2022 from 09h00 to 13h00 at Protea Hotel by Marriott Midrand, this masterclass will comprehensively cover everything which is property related, from finding the right house to securing a bond. A great team of experts will also be on hand to answer any questions you may have about the process. Insights which will be discussed during this event include how to use the Private Property App to find your perfect home, how to make an Offer to Purchase for the first time (OTP), how to finance your first property, how to fix a bad credit record, how to deal with the municipality when buying a home, legal and cost intricasies of property purchasing,etc. You must attend this event for you to gain the confidence and knowledge to make your dream a reality. 